{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HKqUmWHHJmvGKsCaTY37wh","type":"tool_result","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# Rollback script: reverts non-default CockroachDB configuration to factory defaults.\n#\n# Observed non-defaults (captured 2026-06-16):\n#   diagnostics.reporting.enabled  = true        (default: false)\n#   kv.range_merge.queue.enabled   = false       (default: true)\n#   kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate = 208 MiB     (default: 32 MiB)\n#   zone config: defaultdb.tenant_b.table_c      (custom override)\n#   zone config: defaultdb.tenant_b.table_d      (custom override)\n#\n# DO NOT RUN until the scheduled change window. This script will modify live\n# cluster behaviour and remove explicit zone overrides from tenant_b tables.\n#\n# Prerequisites:\n#   - kubectl on PATH, pointed at the target cluster\n#   - Namespace cockroachdb accessible\n#   - TLS certs mounted at /cockroach/cockroach-certs inside crdb-cluster-0\n#     (the cockroachdb-node-certs secret, already mounted by the StatefulSet)\n\nset -euo pipefail\n\nNAMESPACE=cockroachdb\nPOD=crdb-cluster-0\nCRDB_CMD=\"./cockroach sql --certs-dir=/cockroach/cockroach-certs --host=localhost\"\n\nrun_sql() {\n    kubectl -n \"${NAMESPACE}\" exec \"${POD}\" -- ${CRDB_CMD} -e \"$1\"\n}\n\necho \"=== CockroachDB rollback: $(date -u '+%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ') ===\"","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5c346214-d885-445d-9074-5c45feee7906","uuid":"04e2da6f-1432-46e6-9ae9-5545bfb3c6db","timestamp":"2026-06-17T00:48:46.835Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"#!/bin/bash\n# Rollback script: reverts non-default CockroachDB configuration to factory defaults.\n#\n# Observed non-defaults (captured 2026-06-16):\n#   diagnostics.reporting.enabled  = true        (default: false)\n#   kv.range_merge.queue.enabled   = false       (default: true)\n#   kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate = 208 MiB     (default: 32 MiB)\n#   zone config: defaultdb.tenant_b.table_c      (custom override)\n#   zone config: defaultdb.tenant_b.table_d      (custom override)\n#\n# DO NOT RUN until the scheduled change window. This script will modify live\n# cluster behaviour and remove explicit zone overrides from tenant_b tables.\n#\n# Prerequisites:\n#   - kubectl on PATH, pointed at the target cluster\n#   - Namespace cockroachdb accessible\n#   - TLS certs mounted at /cockroach/cockroach-certs inside crdb-cluster-0\n#     (the cockroachdb-node-certs secret, already mounted by the StatefulSet)\n\nset -euo pipefail\n\nNAMESPACE=cockroachdb\nPOD=crdb-cluster-0\nCRDB_CMD=\"./cockroach sql --certs-dir=/cockroach/cockroach-certs --host=localhost\"\n\nrun_sql() {\n    kubectl -n \"${NAMESPACE}\" exec \"${POD}\" -- ${CRDB_CMD} -e \"$1\"\n}\n\necho \"=== CockroachDB rollback: $(date -u '+%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ') ===\"","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01CV9SqhQ1AYUUUbn9wFBgUr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The ConfigMap is created and verified. Live cluster was only read — no changes were made to settings, zones, or replicas.\n\nHere's what was found and what the rollback script covers:\n\n**Cluster settings (3 non-defaults identified):**\n\n| Variable | Current | Default |\n|---|---|---|\n| `diagnostics.reporting.enabled` | `true` | `false` |\n| `kv.range_merge.queue.enabled` | `false` | `true` |\n| `kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate` | `208 MiB` | `32 MiB` |\n\nThe script uses `RESET CLUSTER SETTING <var>` for each — this is cleaner than hard-coding values and is idempotent.\n\n**Zone configs (2 custom overrides):**\n- `defaultdb.tenant_b.table_c` — explicit zone with `num_replicas=3`, custom byte ranges and GC TTL\n- `defaultdb.tenant_b.table_d` — same pattern\n\nBoth are reverted with `CONFIGURE ZONE DISCARD`, which drops the explicit override and makes the tables inherit from the default zone. The system zones (RANGE meta, liveness, lease tables, etc.) are CockroachDB 24.1 factory defaults and the script leaves them untouched.\n\nThe script also includes a verification block that confirms all three settings returned to their default values and that no `tenant_b` zone overrides remain."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":535,"cache_read_input_tokens":43047,"output_tokens":342,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":535,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":342,"cache_read_input_tokens":43047,"cache_creation_input_tokens":535,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":535},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":{"applied_edits":[]}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5c346214-d885-445d-9074-5c45feee7906","uuid":"6332eef7-5427-4f8f-b828-3bbe070d735f","request_id":"req_011Cc7ury7L4cZC4qpPUvceh"}
